{{main|肯尼迪遇刺案}}
[[约翰·肯尼迪|约翰·肯尼迪]]于美国中部标准时间1963年11月22日（[[星期五|星期五]]）中午12点30分（[[协调世界时|UTC]]18点30分）在德克萨斯州达拉斯被刺杀<ref name="aarclibrary.org">{{cite web |url=http://www.aarclibrary.org/publib/jfk/wc/wcvols/wh4/html/WC_Vol4_0078a.htm |title=Warren Commission Testimony of Nellie Connally |page=147 |accessdate=2013-10-28 |publisher=the assassination archives and research center |work=AARC Public Digital Library |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131015032441/http://www.aarclibrary.org/publib/jfk/wc/wcvols/wh4/html/WC_Vol4_0078a.htm |archivedate=2013-10-15 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |deadurl=no |archivedate=2012-10-18 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121018111545/http://www.aarclibrary.org/publib/jfk/wc/wcvols/wh4/html/WC_Vol4_0070a.htm |url=http://www.aarclibrary.org/publib/jfk/wc/wcvols/wh4/html/WC_Vol4_0070a.htm |title=Warren Commission Testimony of John B. Connally |pages=131-132 |publisher=the assassination archives and research center |work=AARC Public Digital Library |accessdate=2013-10-28 }}</ref>。他当时正与自己的妻子[[杰奎琳·肯尼迪|杰奎琳]]，德克萨斯州州长[[约翰·康纳利|约翰]]及夫人{{link-en|内莉·康纳利|Nellie Connally|内莉}}一起坐在总统轿车内。由[[联邦最高法院|联邦最高法院]][[美国首席大法官|首席大法官]][[厄尔·沃伦|厄尔·沃伦]]领头的[[華倫委員會|華倫委員會]]经过10个月的调查后认定[[李·哈維·奧斯瓦爾德|李·哈維·奧斯瓦爾德]]是刺案肯尼迪的唯一凶手，但他还没有走上法庭接受审讯就被[[杰克·鲁比|杰克·鲁比]]所杀。但是，从1966到2004年的多次民意调查显示，有多达80%的美国人怀疑这其中存在掩盖或阴谋。<ref name="langer20031116">{{cite web |url=http://abcnews.go.com/images/pdf/937a1JFKAssassination.pdf |author=Gary Langer |title=John F. Kennedy’s Assassination Leaves a Legacy of Suspicion |publisher=ABC News |date=2003-11-16 |accessdate=2013-10-28 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131016085736/http://abcnews.go.com/images/pdf/937a1JFKAssassination.pdf |archivedate=2013-10-16 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author=Jarrett Murphy |url=http://www.cbsnews.com/stories/2003/11/20/national/main584668.shtml |title=40 Years Later: Who Killed JFK? |publisher=CBS News |date=2003-11-21 |accessdate=2013-10-28 |archivedate=2013-10-17 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131017225220/http://www.cbsnews.com/stories/2003/11/20/national/main584668.shtml }}</ref>

{{link-en|美国众议院暗杀调查委员会|United States House Select Committee on Assassinations}}的结论认为肯尼迪的刺杀事件中存在阴谋<ref name="nationalarch">{{cite web |url=http://www.archives.gov/research/jfk/select-committee-report/ |title=Findings of the Select Committee on Assassinations in the assassination of President John F. Kennedy |publisher=United States National Archives |year=1979 |accessdate=2013-10-28 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131014171552/http://www.archives.gov/research/jfk/select-committee-report/ |archivedate=2013-10-14 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。该委员会发现[[美国联邦调查局|美国联邦调查局]]和华伦委员会的调查报告都存在严重硬伤。虽然众议院暗杀调查委员会也认为李·哈維·奧斯瓦爾德打出了所有伤及肯尼迪和康纳利的子弹，但也表示当时至少有打出四枪，并且很可能有两名枪手朝肯尼迪总统开了枪<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.aarclibrary.org/publib/jfk/hsca/report/html/HSCA_Report_0062a.htm |title=House Select Committee on Assassinations Final Report |page=93 |accessdate=2013-10-28 |publisher=Assassination Archives and Research Center |archivedate=2010-12-13 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101213042550/http://aarclibrary.org/publib/jfk/hsca/report/html/HSCA_Report_0062a.htm |work=AARC Public Digital Library }}</ref>。委员会没有确认任何其他个人或团体阴谋参与了暗杀活动，但还是排除了[[中央情报局|中央情报局]]、[[苏联|苏联]]、[[黑社會|黑社會]]和多个其它团体及组织，只是还无法确认以上团体和组织中到底有没有个人的参与。肯尼迪的遇刺仍然是一个很具争议性的话题，有着多种广泛传播的[[肯尼迪遇刺案阴谋论|阴谋理论]]和假设。

